This directory vendors the minimal Dirtybird v1.14 descriptor suffix-array
bridge used by the optional `dero-astrobwt/v114` feature.

Descriptor suffix array:
  Files: dluna_v114.h, v114_stubs.cpp, v114_wrapper.cpp, sha_stub.c,
         openssl/sha.h
